Title: All links are clickable and lead to valid pages
Steps: 1. Navigate to https://www.unosquare.com 2. Click every link on the page
Expected Result: Each link opens the correct page without errors

Title: All buttons are clickable
Steps: 1. Navigate to https://www.unosquare.com 2. Click every button on the page
Expected Result: Each button is clickable and triggers its expected action

Title: All images load successfully
Steps: 1. Navigate to https://www.unosquare.com 2. Check every image on the page
Expected Result: All images load without broken links (status < 400)

Title: Search box works if present
Steps: 1. Navigate to https://www.unosquare.com 2. Locate the search box 3. Enter 'test' and submit
Expected Result: Search results page loads or results are displayed
